 072.png
DESCRIPTION:This event is one of 16+ events participating in a statewide d
 ay of action to protest immigrant detention centers in Indiana. It will ad
 dress the nearby detention center commonly referred to as the "Speedway Sl
 ammer." May is when all eyes are on the Speedway in Indianapolis\, and thi
 s event will have increased visibility. Join us as we say NO to unjustly d
 etaining our immigrant friends and neighbors. For this event\, please plan
  to stand with our group at the southwest corner of 16th street and Ma
LOCATION:4904 W 16th St\, Indianapolis\, IN\, 46224
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisiblecentralindiana/event/948271/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Central Indiana (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
